data.name: txt_One.Text
data.value:
First, start by selecting the amount you wish to bet and place the bet by clicking on the chip.
Once the chip is clicked, an arrow would appear where the betting can be placed.
Do not forget that the bet amount can be changed using the mouse wheel.
After selecting the desired betting amount, place your bet either on the Pass Line or the Don't Pass Line and hit the "Roll" button.
